# AlphaSwarm Orchestrator Model
# Register with: ollama create alphaswarm-orchestrator -f modelfiles/Modelfile.orchestrator
# Base: qwen3.6:27b-q4_K_M — Q4_K_M dodges the IQ4_XS Metal kernel regression
# (~3.8x slowdown on Apple Silicon). num_ctx trimmed from qwen3.6's 262144
# default to 8192 to keep KV cache manageable. Reasoning is default-on in
# qwen3.6; call sites pass think=False per 41.4-MODEL-DECISION-LOG.md.
FROM qwen3.6:27b-q4_K_M
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER num_gpu 999
